
REST Routes:

---Categories---:
GET /api/categories - Get all categories
POST /api/categories - Create a new category
GET /api/categories/:categoryId - Get specific category information
PUT /api/categories/:categoryId - Update category information
DELETE /api/categories/:categoryId - Delete a category

---Tasks---:
GET /api/categories/:categoryId/tasks - Get all tasks within a category
POST /api/categories/:categoryId/tasks - Create a new task within a category
GET /api/categories/:categoryId/tasks/:taskId - Get specific task information within a category
PUT /api/categories/:categoryId/tasks/:taskId - Update task information
DELETE /api/categories/:categoryId/tasks/:taskId - Delete a task

---Task actions---:
POST /api/categories/:categoryId/tasks/:taskId/complete - Mark a task as complete


Frontend Routing URLs:

---Categories---:
/categories - List of all categories
/categories/:categoryId - Specific category
      NOT USED      /categories/:categoryId/edit - Edit category

---Tasks---:
/categories/:categoryId/tasks - List of all tasks within a category
      NOT USED      /categories/:categoryId/tasks/:taskId - Specific task


